    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界观</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘的魔力溢出在洞窟中……冒险者们聚集魔力晶石，向着洞窟最深处的“魔力核心”进发。然而，这股魔力会将人类凝聚在一起，还是会带来繁荣？为了找到答案，玩家将挑战洞窟！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实时卡牌战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318090/extras/230520566c965652bfd1fb67174a3a85.avif?t=1738755001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318090/extras_big/230520566c965652bfd1fb67174a3a85.avif?t=1738755001 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《EvilMana》中，战斗以实时方式进行！资源恢复、敌人行动以及阶段推进都会随着时间流逝而发生。享受这种紧张刺激的战斗吧，一瞬间的决定可能决定胜负！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318090/extras/ad7099bf875d6bddd4e61ad4ebe64390.avif?t=1738755001\" width=540 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险从1级开始，每次升级都会随机提升某个属性！每个属性都会对战斗和探索产生重大影响，因此制定适合当前属性的策略非常重要！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >称号</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318090/extras/b4c0b8c445215d1b1ae8feb325c52db0.avif?t=1738755001\" width=672 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过冒险达成成就，解锁称号并装备在旅途中。这些称号将赋予各种奖励，如属性提升、特殊卡牌邂逅，甚至能够引导更强大的法力之力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >卡组构建</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过100种普通卡牌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败BOSS获得的奖励卡牌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过50种遗物</p></li></ul>",
